■ Whenever this creature attacks, you may cast a colorless spell that costs 7 or less from your graveyard for no cost. Then put it on the bottom of your deck.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
{RIGHT GOD LINK} (As you put this creature into the battle zone, you may link this creature to a God that has "Center God Link" or "Left God Link". The linked god gets each god's characteristics (power and abilities) and becomes one creature. When the linked creature would leave the battle zone, choose one side instead.)

■ Each turn, you may untap this creature the first time it is tapped.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
{LEFT GOD LINK} (As you put this creature into the battle zone, you may link this creature to a God that has "Center God Link" or "Right God Link". The linked god gets each god's characteristics (power and abilities) and becomes one creature. When the linked creature would leave the battle zone, choose one side instead.)

■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, put all cards from your deck except the bottom 5 into your graveyard.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you would draw the last card of your deck, you may return a card from your graveyard to your hand instead.
